---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 153
  - Title: Tejo-bindu Upanishad
    Location: I 17
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
---
Abstinence is the bringing of the senses under control through the knowledge
that ‘all is the Brahman’. This abstinence should constantly be practised.
